{"sections":{"main":{"type":"article-template","custom_css":[".article .section-header__title {text-transform: none;}"],"settings":{"image_hero":false,"blog_show_tags":true,"blog_show_date":false,"blog_show_comments":true,"blog_show_author":false,"social_sharing_blog":true}},"blog-posts":{"type":"blog-posts","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"You may also like","blog":"","post_limit":3,"blog_show_tags":false,"blog_show_date":true,"blog_show_comments":false,"blog_show_author":false,"view_all":true,"blog_image_size":"wide","divider":false}},"text_and_image_7eqY8J":{"type":"text-and-image","custom_css":[".feature-row {align-items: start;}"],"name":"t:sections.text-and-image.presets.image_with_text.name","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/18a18dc7d1eb8798bd3b6a03171c315d81d6e59a.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<h4>The Rise of Statement Earrings in Men's Luxury Jewelry\u2028<\/h4><p>Men’s fashion is embracing bold accessories, with statement earrings—especially gold hoop earrings and black hoop earrings—becoming must-have pieces in contemporary style. This trend reflects a broader movement toward expressive, personalized fashion, where accessories are no longer just subtle details but defining elements of a man’s look.<\/p><p><\/p><h4>Black Hoops: Bold and Edgy<br\/><\/h4><p>For those who prefer a bolder approach, men's black earrings make a daring yet stylish statement. The Acies Collection is designed for men who embrace individuality and modern luxury, featuring silver hoops with black enamel, and even black diamond accents. These elements bring depth and boldness, making them ideal for those looking to push fashion boundaries.<\/p><p><\/p>","html":"","button_label":"EXPLORE ACIES HOOPS","button_link":"#","button_labels":"","button_links":"","imaget":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/9b854df0b92787089d58829e43e781753bf43e4d.jpg","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"right","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"text_and_image_ChbmHr":{"type":"text-and-image","name":"t:sections.text-and-image.presets.image_with_text.name","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5300a48dda622841288524163ab32022abf415b2.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<h4>Everyday Hoops: For a Casual Look\u2028<\/h4><p>For a more laid-back, everyday look, the Ulysses Collection offers hoop earrings that provide a touch of luxury without feeling over-the-top. These pieces are designed with comfort and simplicity in mind, making them perfect for daily wear. Whether you're out for a coffee, hitting the gym, or just going for a casual stroll, Ulysses gold hoops can easily complement any outfit, from a t-shirt and jeans to a more refined casual look.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","html":"","button_label":"GO TO COLLECTION","button_link":"#","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"right","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"background_image_text_NbwyJd":{"type":"background-image-text","name":"t:sections.background-image-text.presets.large_image_with_text_box.name","settings":{"classes":"","subtitle":"","title":"","text":"<h4>How to Wear Men’s Hoop Earrings<\/h4><p>Minimalist Look: A single gold or black hoop earring with a sleek all-black outfit.<br\/>Layering & Stacking: Mix gold hoop earrings for men with black hoop earrings for contrast.<br\/>Statement Styling: Pair hoops with a black gold cross necklace and a gladiator ring with black diamonds for a powerful aesthetic.<br\/>Casual vs. Formal: Keep it subtle with small gold hoops for work, or go bold with big black hoop earrings for streetwear styling.<\/p>","text_color":"#ffffff","button_label":"","butt